        <mxCell id="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--7" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It monitors the bitcoin network for IPC-related transactions, such as &lt;i&gt;createChild()&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;joinSubnet()&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;deposit()&lt;/i&gt;, and &lt;i&gt;propagate().&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="660" y="376" width="220" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--10" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;We run a bitcoin full node, connected to a local testnet.&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="660" y="526" width="220" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--12" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It creates the required bitcoin transactions (e.g, to implement the &lt;i&gt;createChild()&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;joinSubnet()&lt;/i&gt; functionalities) and submits them over PRC to the local bitcoin node.&lt;/font&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="660" y="446" width="220" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-1" value="IPC L1 Manager" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;shadow=0;glass=0;fillStyle=solid;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="920" y="370" width="200" height="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-3" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It keeps track of IPC-related state on bitcoin, such as existing subnets and their parameteers, and exposes an interface for modiying it (e.g., create new subnet, join an existing).&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="660" y="280" width="220" height="85" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-7" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0;entryDx=220;entryDy=40;entryPerimeter=0;dashed=1;" parent="1" source="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-1" target="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-3" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-10" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.25;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0;entryDx=220;entryDy=45;entryPerimeter=0;dashed=1;" parent="1" source="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--6" target="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--12" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tbgbCJuzEw6YqtSzz_3i-12" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.25;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0;entryDx=220;entryDy=20;entryPerimeter=0;dashed=1;" parent="1" source="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--2" target="7knJM6DkiD1VyGRECrS--10" edge="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tgi2q5tbjGthcWReG4RT-1" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;State: accounts and balances&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;Interface: create_account(), transfer(), withdraw(), create_state_checkpoint().&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;It contains all IPC-subnet logic for handling incoming messages and creating outward messages, such as MintDeposited(), Withdraw().&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Stage 1&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;this is instantiated by a Simulator, which is a mock implementation that handles/creates the required messages.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Stage 2&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;this will be Fendermint.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontColor=#666600;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1361" y="295" width="190" height="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
